instruction: Make a list of items that would be needed to go on a camping trip
output:
A camping trip requires a variety of equipment and supplies, including:
• Tent 
• Sleeping bag 
• Sleeping pad
• Flashlight 
• Matches/lighter 
• Camp stove 
• Cooking utensils/pans 
• Cooler 
• Firewood 
• Portable chairs
• Portable tables 
• Insect repellent 
• First aid kit 
• Map and compass 
• Potable water 
• Sunscreen 
• Food items 
• Extra clothing 
• Camping tools (trowel, ax, etc.) 
• Water shoes 
• Toiletries 
• Trash bags 
• Pet items (if applicable)
